<P>
 BMG to Distribute Crystal Dynamics' Multimedia: BMG International will make 
its first foray into multimedia distribution with interactive games produced by 
Crystal Dynamics, the two firms said. Under the deal, BMG will handle marketing 
and distribution for Crystal and for Star Interactive -- a multimedia 
publishing start-up still in the planning stages which will have an exclusive 
