 Prices Up at Second Acid Rain Credits Auction: Proponents of market-based 
environmental rules praised the results, announced by the Chicago Board of 
Trade, of the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency's second annual auction of 
rights to emit acid-rain forming pollution. CBOT officials and the 
